rust-fern (0.6.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Team upload.
  * Package fern 0.6.1 from crates.io using debcargo 2.5.0
  * Update no-syslog34.patch and no-reopen.patch for new upstream
  * Drop use-tempfile-instead-of-tempdir.patch, upstream has switched
  * Adjust dependency on colored to version 2

 -- Peter Michael Green <plugwash@debian.org>  Sat, 21 May 2022 19:41:12 +0000

rust-fern (0.6.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Team upload.
  * Package fern 0.6.0 from crates.io using debcargo 2.5.0
  * Remove optional (in the Cargo sense) dependency on reopen
    It is not packaged in Debian.
  * Use tempfile instead of tempdir for tests, the latter is
    not packaged in Debian.
  * Disable the "syslog3" example, and convert the "syslog"
    example to syslog 6.
  * Improve the syslog 6 patch to actually provide a working
    feature rather than a feature that does nothing.

 -- Peter Michael Green <plugwash@debian.org>  Sat, 25 Dec 2021 22:42:37 +0000

